{"tid":1543071,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣先可以令到領養返黎成犬有安全感？","createTime":"2019-09-05T05:10:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T06:50:49.000Z","uid":145579,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"d6ebf97db528ff851ffd724752bf13ab5a14d3ab","tid":1543071,"uid":145579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T05:10:43.000Z","msg":"前排領養左隻成犬，狗狗係繁殖場救出黎，由細都係個籠入面冇出過街冇接觸過陌生人所以搞到狗狗非常細膽，摸佢抱佢會震到猫王咁，要係個籠入面佢先覺得安全。留意左佢一排，佢係個籠入面會眼甘甘咁望住你去到邊望到邊，同佢對望佢眼神唔會避同埋佢要屋企完全冇人先肯食野同去廁所，最慘係佢每2日先食一次野每2日先去一次廁所。<br />\n<br />\n想問下大家點先可以俾到佢知屋企係安全，屋企人係錫佢。我試過用零食引佢佢完全唔理唔食，玩具又唔玩，唔好話出街呀佢連個籠都唔夠出黎。仲有咩方法可以建立對我既信心，可以令佢有正常狗狗生活！？<br />\n<br />\n謝謝"},{"pid":"97cbdbc97538de3b454de063b50fcc8041561c68","tid":1543071,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T05:10:49.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EAUpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EAUpQ.jpg&h=30bf1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUE1PYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUE1PYa.jpg&h=d8331036&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1sNZBDb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1sNZBDb.jpg&h=ace5c24e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8KM7Lwx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8KM7Lwx.jpg&h=5719ebc4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SoyFk4T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSoyFk4T.jpg&h=2bffae59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SsV05wz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSsV05wz.jpg&h=d54e941c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EUH604U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEUH604U.jpg&h=74590733&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a8089796a6113afafaa4f685bbd7c132f7497dd","tid":1543071,"uid":130271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T05:15:31.000Z","msg":"用手親自餵食<br />\n咁樣隻狗就會當你係飼主 自然會同你親近啲"},{"pid":"31f3aa21a76a0739cbe7fce5b489d4a1a3248c29","tid":1543071,"uid":57862,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T05:17:27.000Z","msg":"養多隻<br />\n不推文 thx"},{"pid":"b6d9e8829487e843048ee5c346212779c46da5df","tid":1543071,"uid":148332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T05:17:34.000Z","msg":"耐性,真誠"},{"pid":"16533b10ddfde96b0b677a16b9a7fb00cadabf7a","tid":1543071,"uid":294782,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T05:24:20.000Z","msg":"最主要應該都係比時間佢, 佢習慣係個籠度, 你未友佢<br />\n長期打開個籠, 佢想出就出入就入, 唔好迫佢出黎, 你慢慢餵佢食飯, 自然會同你熟, 你係屋企冇野做, 睇書玩手機果d時間, 試下坐係佢隔離做呢d野, 陪多d佢<br />\n如果你全家都準備出街冇人, 試下放野食係籠外半米, 睇下佢夠唔夠膽行出黎食, 慢慢越拉越遠<br />\n如果佢係冇人先肯食野同便便既, 你試下用布圍住個籠大半, 比番d安全感佢"},{"pid":"5a6b88e8ec9f19506c63cc00195592d13c17250e","tid":1543071,"uid":219079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T05:24:41.000Z","msg":"時間問題<br />\n多啲陪下佢<br />\n坐係佢隔離同佢傾下計<br />\n<br />\n如果要摸佢 <br />\n可以非常非常慢咁伸隻手過去<br />\n比佢聞下隻手先<br />\n再慢慢用手指liuliu下<br />\n再慢慢用成隻手"},{"pid":"5863aee823e8ccf912c3f90a5ac6d5b24587fb88","tid":1543071,"uid":145579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a8089796a6113afafaa4f685bbd7c132f7497dd","tid":1543071,"uid":130271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T05:15:31.000Z","msg":"用手親自餵食<br />\n咁樣隻狗就會當你係飼主 自然會同你親近啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T05:25:40.000Z","msg":"佢連零食都唔食 我都想親自餵"},{"pid":"a74580ce39b103827c3f2ff1911b736a51381d01","tid":1543071,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T05:26:37.000Z","msg":"投入，愛護"},{"pid":"8db38e98e69eb5d19ec2d7047ef436dbf535026a","tid":1543071,"uid":100772,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T05:26:55.000Z","msg":"打佢"},{"pid":"e7843aa4062f9a4f5d9c9534b5a8025717ccd483","tid":1543071,"uid":37234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T05:27:08.000Z","msg":"要係個籠入面先覺得安全，以為你講緊香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2c57639b13a0dda4ff2ef0ba1b9c5e93bbce9c2","tid":1543071,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T05:29:56.000Z","msg":"對住佢做既動作要慢啲 我之前喺佢面前正常速度拎起塊尿墊佢都驚 有聲又驚 但慢慢拎同放就冇事"},{"pid":"22505fb5d4bb16662a47638aebacf7217df2e86a","tid":1543071,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T05:30:34.000Z","msg":"攬佢，同佢玩"},{"pid":"2fde051dd05fdb4b20ff62061620d4857228e1b9","tid":1543071,"uid":268725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T05:30:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8B39Niu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8B39Niu.png&h=c9eeccd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3fcb3d14d943fda5e00b2b70b07621009e6a2db","tid":1543071,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T05:31:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"39ee4de116a848ed2f54aed3abc0b70a79181741","tid":1543071,"uid":145579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3fcb3d14d943fda5e00b2b70b07621009e6a2db","tid":1543071,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit